#### PR description:

This is a follow up of #43857 . Here ```DQM/SiOuterTracker``` & ```Validation/SiOuterTrackerV``` are removed. All the plugins have already been moved to corresponding package with names ```SiTrackerPhase2``` in #43857 .

Not needed.
